Additional IP Rights Grant (Patents)

The upstream libvpx project includes an additional patent grant for WebM codec
implementations. The frozen baseline for this repository is libvpx v1.16.0:

https://chromium.googlesource.com/webm/libvpx/+/refs/tags/v1.16.0/PATENTS

When source code is ported from libvpx, keep this file with distributions of
libgopx and review the upstream grant text for exact legal terms.
